{"type": "article", "id": 27097, "title": "深海桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-20T06:55:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 145, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162511aiw3K8kUXyBDCIGj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>提起夏天，不少人会想到大海，最近罗马尼亚的设计师 Eduard Locota 就以此为灵感，打造了一款像是把海水锁起来的桌子。它的桌面由有机玻璃制成，浅绿到深蓝的变化与真实的海洋别无二致。与白色大理石雕刻而成的三足底座搭配后，营造出一种流动感，非常精致。这张漂亮的深海桌全球限量 35 张，可以通过 Locota 的个人网站<a href=\"http://eduardlocota.com/product/delmare-table/\">进行订购</a>，根据不同尺寸，定价为 4900 至 15500 欧元不等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162508XmBvsoLpngJExra4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162508KfdC3H4QvspxMUl8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162509CVdFjvfn34lEka2A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021625099zNPwscl4LmYAbWo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}